<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/BDJ.12.e115422.figure3>
    dc:description "Figure 3. Habitats of Pytho abieticola J. R. Sahlberg, 1875 in Lithuania: a, b Sesuva Reserve (N 54.934772 E 24.252475), Kaisiadorys District Municipality; c, d Punios silas (N 54.545196 E 24.022972), Alytus District Municipality; e, f Punios silas (N 54.545055, E 24.030973), Alytus District Municipality. Note the flight interception trap in photos d-e (photos a & b - Romas Ferenca, c-f - Vytautas Tamutis)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/930384" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

